title: Shadow Government Holds Liberty Hostage in Bombshell Political Cartoon
text:
Shadow Government Holds Liberty Hostage in Bombshell Political Cartoon Trump and shadow government clash intensifies Infowars.com - February 17, 2017 Comments 
Political cartoonist Ben Garrison is back at it again with his latest hard-hitting piece on current events in the United States. 
Garrison is now taking on the “shadow government” as President Trump and the national security apparatus battle for dominance in the public sphere. 
— BenGarrison Cartoons (@GrrrGraphics) February 17, 2017 
The “shadow,” represented by numerous entities within the power structure, can be seen holding a knife to Uncle Sam’s throat.
